Package com.onlineStoreCom.entity.product

Class Product

java.lang.Object
com.onlineStoreCom.entity.setting.subsetting.IdBasedEntity
com.onlineStoreCom.entity.product.Product
@Entity public class Product extends IdBasedEntity
Entity class representing a product in the online store.

This class represents a product with its details, pricing, inventory information, and relationships with categories and brands. It also manages product images and details.
